You have learned to tend to your eldritch court and garner favor with eldritch entities. Whenever you perform a signficant action or make an offering which is in the purview of one of the entities in your //Court// you may pay ''1x Eldritch'' to gain a point of //Favor// with that entity. Favor may be spent in any interaction with the entity, including calling upon it to perform //Invocations// granting a +1d bonus per point of favor spent.